<p class="MsoNormal"><a name="_7197d0e6-f6c2-b54e-3764-dbccf205caa4" id="_7197d0e6-f6c2-b54e-3764-dbccf205caa4"></a><a href="http://www.opengis.net/spec/emissionml/1.0">http://www.opengis.net/spec/emissionml/1.0</a></p>

