        <div><a name="_82b58f8a-e326-7dc2-f9b9-578930a606d8" id="_82b58f8a-e326-7dc2-f9b9-578930a606d8"></a><h2>7.4.<span style="mso-tab-count:1">&#xA0; </span>Source Type Class</h2>

