      <div class="Section3">
        <a name="_8b3b2b04-6bbc-f893-3a1c-47ba848d31c4" id="_8b3b2b04-6bbc-f893-3a1c-47ba848d31c4"></a>
        <h1 class="Annex"><b>Annex A</b><br/>(informative)<br/><b>Conformance Class Abstract Test Suite (Normative)</b></h1>
        <div><a name="_e3e7210d-8414-3c3a-9c22-90523b26486d" id="_e3e7210d-8414-3c3a-9c22-90523b26486d"></a><h2>A.1.<span style="mso-tab-count:1">&#xA0; </span>Abstract tests for Emission Event Conceptual Data Model Core</h2>

<div><a name="_8aa75767-0b57-c15a-80b3-fa2e9bab3da5" id="_8aa75767-0b57-c15a-80b3-fa2e9bab3da5"></a><h3>A.1.1.<span style="mso-tab-count:1">&#xA0; </span>Emission Event Conceptual Data Model Core</h3>

<p class="TableTitle" style="text-align:center;">Table A.1</p><div align="center" class="table_container"><table class="MsoISOTable" style="mso-table-anchor-horizontal:column;mso-table-overlap:never;border-spacing:0;border-width:1px;" width="90%"><a name="_71be8bf2-66f0-c2fa-f6a2-78ae0abaf27a" id="_71be8bf2-66f0-c2fa-f6a2-78ae0abaf27a"></a><colgroup><col width="20%"/><col width="80%"/></colgroup><tbody><tr><td valign="middle" align="left" style="border-top:solid windowtext 1.5pt;mso-border-top-alt:solid windowtext 1.5pt;border-bottom:solid windowtext 1.0pt;mso-border-bottom-alt:solid windowtext 1.0pt;page-break-after:avoid;" width="20.0%">Conformance class</td><td valign="middle" align="left" style="border-top:solid windowtext 1.5pt;mso-border-top-alt:solid windowtext 1.5pt;border-bottom:solid windowtext 1.0pt;mso-border-bottom-alt:solid windowtext 1.0pt;page-break-after:avoid;" width="80.0%">/conf/datamodel/core</td></tr><tr><td valign="middle" align="left" style="border-top:none;mso-border-top-alt:none;border-bottom:solid windowtext 1.0pt;mso-border-bottom-alt:solid windowtext 1.0pt;page-break-after:avoid;" width="20.0%">Requirements</td><td valign="middle" align="left" style="border-top:none;mso-border-top-alt:none;border-bottom:solid windowtext 1.0pt;mso-border-bottom-alt:solid windowtext 1.0pt;page-break-after:avoid;" width="80.0%">/req/datamodel/core</td></tr><tr><td valign="middle" align="left" style="border-top:none;mso-border-top-alt:none;border-bottom:solid windowtext 1.0pt;mso-border-bottom-alt:solid windowtext 1.0pt;page-break-after:avoid;" width="20.0%">Test purpose</td><td valign="middle" align="left" style="border-top:none;mso-border-top-alt:none;border-bottom:solid windowtext 1.0pt;mso-border-bottom-alt:solid windowtext 1.0pt;page-break-after:avoid;" width="80.0%">Verify that all requirements from the requirements class have been fulfilled.</td></tr><tr><td valign="middle" align="left" style="border-top:none;mso-border-top-alt:none;border-bottom:solid windowtext 1.0pt;mso-border-bottom-alt:solid windowtext 1.0pt;page-break-after:avoid;" width="20.0%">Test method</td><td valign="middle" align="left" style="border-top:none;mso-border-top-alt:none;border-bottom:solid windowtext 1.0pt;mso-border-bottom-alt:solid windowtext 1.0pt;page-break-after:avoid;" width="80.0%">Inspect the documentation of the application, schema or profile.</td></tr><tr><td valign="middle" align="left" style="border-top:none;mso-border-top-alt:none;border-bottom:solid windowtext 1.5pt;mso-border-bottom-alt:solid windowtext 1.5pt;page-break-after:auto;" width="20.0%">Test type</td><td valign="middle" align="left" style="border-top:none;mso-border-top-alt:none;border-bottom:solid windowtext 1.5pt;mso-border-bottom-alt:solid windowtext 1.5pt;page-break-after:auto;" width="80.0%">Capability</td></tr></tbody></table></div>
